# Icons and Buttons

## Icons
- All icons use the accent green color (`var(--accent)` / #00e5a8) to match the tab icons.
- Icons are styled via: `.btn i`, `.icon-prefix`, `.collapsible-icon`, `.tab-btn i`, `.notification-card h3 i`.

## Buttons
- **Every button must have an icon** (Font Awesome 6) before the label.
- Use `aria-hidden="true"` on decorative icons.
- Icon + text format: `<i class="fa-solid fa-icon-name" aria-hidden="true"></i> Label`

### Common icon mappings
- Update/Refresh: `fa-arrows-rotate`
- Search: `fa-magnifying-glass`
- Show all/List: `fa-list`
- Clear/Delete: `fa-trash`
- Settings/Filter: `fa-sliders`
- Add user: `fa-user-plus`
- Save/Confirm: `fa-check`
- Cancel: `fa-xmark`
- External link: `fa-up-right-from-square`
- Comment: `fa-comment`
- Copy: `fa-copy`
